> Use your own OpenAI-compatible API endpoint and key

  Optionally set a custom Base URL for an OpenAI-compatible upstream.
  The Base URL is saved to config.toml and the API key to auth.json.
  Leave Base URL empty to use the default OpenAI endpoint.

